public class HoldemSMGroup
extends HoldemHandGroup

A holdem hand group representing sets of starting hands corresponding to Sklansky & Malmuth groups. "SM1" is group 1, etc., with "SM9" defined to be all hands not included in groups 1-8.

Author:
Michael Maurer
